snippet.title: Chocobo's Crystal Tower: Launch Trailer(English)
snippet.description:
"Chocobo" the character from FINAL FANTASY series is now staring on Facebook!!
The game can be played for free! "Chocobo's Crystal Tower" Out Now!
http://apps.facebook.com/chocobos/
* Facebook account required.
*Certain items require a fee for purchase.
